252
00:13:01,563 --> 00:13:05,263
Aku mengandalkanmu, Detektif Kecil.

253
00:13:07,263 --> 00:13:10,063
Jadi, dia adalah kakakmu.

254
00:13:10,063 --> 00:13:11,563
Ya!

255
00:13:11,563 --> 00:13:12,863
Hei.

256
00:13:12,863 --> 00:13:16,463
Dengan kemampuan analisamu,

257
00:13:16,463 --> 00:13:19,963
