297
00:16:53,463 --> 00:16:57,963
selain milik organisasi, virus akan memakan datanya.

298
00:16:57,963 --> 00:16:59,363
Aku benar-benar ceroboh.

299
00:16:59,363 --> 00:17:01,263
Jadi, semua data...

300
00:17:01,263 --> 00:17:04,663
Ya. Semuanya telah lenyap.

301
00:17:04,663 --> 00:17:06,663
Bahkan program komputer.

302
00:17:06,663 --> 00:17:07,963
Apa?

303
00:17:07,963 --> 00:17:09,563
Sial.

304
00:17:15,163 --> 00:17:18,963
Tampaknya aku akan terlibat lama denganmu,

305
00:17:18,963 --> 00:17:20,363
Conan Edogawa.

